    <item>
      <title>密苏里州孕妇不能离婚。批评者称这助长了家庭暴力</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/03/1247838036/divorce-pregnant-women-missouri-abortion-marriage-abuse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该州法律要求寻求离婚的女性披露自己是否怀孕，而州法官不会在怀孕期间最终决定离婚。德克萨斯州和阿肯色州也有类似的法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/03/1247838036/divorce-pregnant-women-missouri-abortion-marriage-abuse</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 09:00:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
